posts.post_title: FS/FT: Looking to sell some sharp T206's with qualifiers
posts.post_content: Please let me know what you might be looking for as I am looking to sell some of my T206's, especially duplicates. Most of them are higher grades, but I do have some low population mid grades with uncommon backs. I also have quite a few low population PSA 6's available, and some PSA higher graded cards with qualifiers (great value for the money)....thanks

Some of the mid grades have backs such as Tolstoi, Brown Hindu, Carolina brights, etc...
